Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================AVANT=================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We chase the birds, stare at the stars and measure the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,just want to divine our ephemeral future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you guide wings, stay close to the etoiles and move the heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall be a precious spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As a part of world from this sandy land,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,light your soul forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,From the mud castle ship, we keep our minds on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Guide us, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}July 2, 93 S.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Benihi (Shirushi)'s funeral has been held.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}She was 29,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}served as a teaching staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We flow the dead into the sea of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Whoever sends the dead at this time must not let the tears sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Because you will be called by the souls sleeping under of the sand, they will beckon you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is the tale handed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you can't cry here Chakuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,or you will be called by the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, clench your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Restrain yourself, Chakuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Restrain, restrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You idoit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I goofed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}My name is Chakuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I am 14 years old, male.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The recording clerk of the {\i1}mud whale{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Many times each time I see off a friendly person,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}my urge to record is increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}According to my grandfather, who was a {\i1}Muin{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I am sickening from an illness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:12.24,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(960,1000)}hypergraphia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}that I can not stop writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The drifting boat on the endless sea of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The population of our mud whale was 513.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Our lives were together with the sand, the wind and the sunlight.
