Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================MAIN==================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get it down slow~ly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it down slow~ly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, everyone's handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys have made a lot of progresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz they have a good teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is better than Chakuro already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tease me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, a {\i1}Shirushi{\i0} shouldn't work as a recording clerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.95,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1206,1000)}sentikinesis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You are wasting your {\i1}thymia{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You were appointed as a recording clerk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,just cuz you're not good at {\i1}thymia{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They are even calling me the destroyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tease yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we were also learning {\i1}thymia{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,from Benihi in this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,forget about Benihi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave ourselves trapped in the death of others,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or we {\i1}Shirushi{\i0} are not able to live through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:35.97,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(1313,1000)}sentikinesis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\i1}Shirushi{\i0} is the name of those who can handle {\i1}thymia{\i0} from emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Nine in ten of the inhabitants of the mud whale are {\i1}Shirushi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We {\i1}Shirushi{\i0} are all like Benihi whom we sent off yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We are all short-lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut some leaves of {\i1}omasa bamboos{\i0} from your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they will be used for food preservation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,pick 5 to 6 new leaves from as tall as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,5 to 6 leaves, 5 to 6 leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said you'd chop the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't run away Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs66}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Close the window, sand's entering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're making your goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For protection from the sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've picked up acrylic boards for us the other day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thatz for you, though it's just a prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The thick body is simply too great for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Decoration is a hobby of this workshop, but it's not that useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As a return, if you find something from the sea or the islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,bring them right here without declaration!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show it off to Sami later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You are wearing cool stuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going out to the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am on my way to Suo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,With your records, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that for the funeral of Benihi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it over writing too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The paper is precious, use it moderately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro's record is useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a diary rather than an official record.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't stop writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm not suit for recording clerk,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wonder if the people who lived in our mud whale
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,could have written more about those happened in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why we came to live on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And why our mud whale does never sink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We may understand these
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,if there are more records left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So I write for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Those who do not have the power of {\i1}thymia{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,such as the chief and the presbyters,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}are called {\i1}Muin{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Most of the {\i1}Shirushi{\i0} die in their twenties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}In the contrast, {\i1}Muin{\i0} are long-living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}They live as the leaders of the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Suo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Chakuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am bringing you the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you cry the whole night last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was crying too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Benihi was a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no emotion recorded in your writings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are very sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's a rule not to write any emotions down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you have to record so many painful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can help you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo is doing researches on extending the lives of {\i1}Shirushi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And you sincerely feel sorrow for our short lives, more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly have shed more tears than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am stupid, writing a lot of records is the only thing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are clever and will have a long live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please solve this world's mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and make people on this ship much much happier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chakuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Here, when people can not hold their emotions on their bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}they clench their fingers in this manner
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}to get their feelings under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}These records will be with you even after I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I hope they can help you in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an adrift island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first adrift island in the past 6 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We have 5 days to go to the island for procurement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, it would become difficult since it will be too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's send a reconnaissance team first tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we will procure goods if it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please scout for a reconnaissance team until tomorrow, Suo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The next morning we left when the sea was calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Chakuro here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope we are not go into troubles this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that Suo chose Sami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know it could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother trusts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}After enter the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}you will sink in the sand if you do not use the {\i1}thymia{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Using {\i1}thymia{\i0} to float the leave boat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}consumes as much stamina as running at full speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Therefore the distance we can arrive is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, never act individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, do not pick anything up since it's recce this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are hot on each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Sami, don't go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But here is different from the islands I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that people used.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}There were islands where we can find something people left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}But we have never found any people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys in the workshop will be happy right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Food?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}She was the first {\i1}human{\i0} I met outside of our mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}If we could call her a {\i1}human{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}considering her status at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She is weakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She is injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She has washed her clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you'd go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's her pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Chakuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost him on the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Masoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to act individually!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said don't pick anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She is not {\i1}anything{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a {\i1}person{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She is weakening, she may die if we leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We interrupted the reconnaissance of the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}and decided to take the girl to the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How beautiful she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami, could you put these clothes on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they are hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.86,SCREEN1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fs54\c&H7B7F8D&\bord1\3c&H5C606C&\pos(969,505)}lykos
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This scar... It seems that she get injured for quite some days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Should I tell others about I was attacted by her with her {\i1}thymia?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Better not I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... It's a sunshower!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Rainwater will be stored in the reservoir of mud whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}very important for our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Also, it was said that rain is auspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely something good is going to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}In our closed little world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}may this girl
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}brings the future unknown to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Everybody in our recce team is excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}For me, the first one who found her, in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't record any emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Aren't you too fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We picked up something terribly good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You are supposed not to take anything back today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will denounce you to the presbytery!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, your puss-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, you muscle idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon and clench your fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna be {\i1}internal moles,{\i0} right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go see it with your own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a person on that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A per... person!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tai.. Taisha-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, she is awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:29.76,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1004,1000)}αὔρα
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,An {\i1}aura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she attack us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here in the mud whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't fight with {\i1}thymia{\i0} or you will be punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Release me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She spoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The same language...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems I've been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, watch your step please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, it's my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the girl from that island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She... Chakuro and Sami have taken her to the medical office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That two brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:24.58,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638.667,1000)}Λύκος
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lykos{\i0}, embroidered on your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos, don't you shock in such an completely unknown place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were you, my heart's throbbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious if I were her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the medical office?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Only young people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They are {\i1}Shirushi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Their abilities of {\i1}thymia{\i0} and stamina decreased after the age of 30 or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people even became bedridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the same in your world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:01.16,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1040,1000)}Φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is here {\i1}Fallaina?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fallaina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}mud whale{\i0} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone calls here like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro, Sami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You have protected this girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the chief here, my name is Taisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute please, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will introduce her to the presbyters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But she is injured and needs medical treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You are kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry, we will take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo, deal with the internal moles please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen? She's the girl on that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can be her friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice to be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo, what's wrong with the internal moles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Since there is a rainbow, they are pardoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni's guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to release them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm just wondering what will they do
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if they know a person has been found on an adrift island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,as a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, Sami should return to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder whether it was caught on that island too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, it follow me itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}In the mud whale, those who breaks the rule
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}would be jailed in an area called the {\i1}internal{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}For some reason, {\i1}thymia{\i0} can not be used there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}For us short-living {\i1}Shirushi{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}it was really sad to lose our freedom and be sent into the internal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}But there were guys who repeat violating the rule
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}and get jailed times and times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Since they have spent so long in the internal,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}they were called the {\i1}internal moles{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an amnesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my body is hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dazzling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We are so honored that the next chief is welcoming us in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not repeat absurd things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure your limited time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the same for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter we are underground or on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In such a small world, nothing is different for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}Muin{\i0} have a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You have enough time to treasure stuffs such as a mud ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something I have to tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we found a person on a adrift island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A person? {\i1}Outside?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not overreact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After all there are worlds outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There are worlds where people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't tell it yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there is another world outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I will leave this trivial ship behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can not tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't depend on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait us, Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Oni is the leader of the internal moles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}It was said that he is the top psychic of {\i1}thymia{\i0} in the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right what I was worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They may do something to Lykos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only Lykos, and the presbyters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me the name of your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been dispatched from the {\i1}home country?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Home country?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please answer my question first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.25,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1040,1000)}Φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is here {\i1}Fallaina?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can not answer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we fully understand your purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we can not reveal our identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems presbyters understand what Lykos is saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was forced to be brought here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your fellows on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I buried them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you feel anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Such as painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.30,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1057,1000)}απάθεια
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She is an {\i1}apatheia{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,People without emotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.54,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(816,1000)}Απάθεια
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apatheia?{\i0} What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is still what it was in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that there is no point in talking with you any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I have to restrain you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It told you to be careful upon your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know what will happen if you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to see her world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys just play with your treasurable mud ship all your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, help...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It must not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make contact with the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the woes will overtake you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni escaped with that island girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursue him as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to her island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You participated in the recce team right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Guide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}There are plenty of things I want to write about the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Stacked sun-dried bricks, painted with mud, we had a toy-like castle city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Lots of people were living there together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I am sure you will be surprised as you are living in an extensive world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}But it was the entirety of our precious world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No matter what occurs,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I am going to write everything happens to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I was determined to keep on writing.
